'''Wli Aworoeɛ Afahyɛ''' yɛ afehyia [[afahyɛ]] a ahenfo ne won manfoɔ a wɔn wɔ Wli a ɛwɔ Frao Mantam mu wɔ Ghana no di. Wɔn a wodi ne Todzi, Agoviefe ne Afegame mpoatam ho fo<ref>http://amedzofevillage.com/en/2016/04/16/323/</ref>. Wodi afahye wɔ Bosome a ɛtɔ so nsɛn mu<ref>https://visitvoltaregion.com/festivals/</ref><ref>https://www.easytrackghana.com/cultural-overview-ghana-festivals.php</ref><ref>https://flygoldstar.com/tour-packages-volta-region.html</ref>. Wli Aworoeɛ da bɛyɛ kilomita 20 firi Hohoe<ref>https://touringghana.com/volta-region/</ref><ref>https://www.fiandadghanalimited.com/wli-falls-festival/</ref>.

== Afahyɛ ==
Wɔ afahyɛ no bere mu, wɔda akokurokosɛm ne nneɛma a woyi kyere adi. Ahenfo ne wɔn manfoɔ no nso de nnaseɛ ma wɔn ho wɔn ho<ref>http://h2829516.stratoserver.net/tourism/index.html</ref><ref>https://viewghana.com/events/wli-falls-festival/</ref>.

== Mfasoɔ ==
Wodi afahyɛ no de da Onyankopon ase sɛ w’ama wɔn aworoeɛ a ɛhɔ daa na ɛma wɔn nsuo wɔ mpɔtam hɔ<ref>https://ghanaemberlin.de/travel-tourism/festival/</ref><ref>https://visitvoltaregion.com/2020/05/26/wli-falls-festival/</ref>.

